trans-unit.source: Learn about the contents of the Windows Phone Silverlight SDK for Azure Mobile Engagement
trans-unit.target: Learn about the contents of the Windows Phone Silverlight SDK for Azure Mobile Engagement

trans-unit.source: This document lists and describes the content deployed by the SDK in your application.
trans-unit.target: This document lists and describes the content deployed by the SDK in your application.

trans-unit.source: This folder contains all the resources that Mobile Engagement needs.
trans-unit.target: This folder contains all the resources that Mobile Engagement needs.

trans-unit.source: You can also customize them to fit your app.
trans-unit.target: You can also customize them to fit your app.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementIconNotification.png` : The brand icon displayed at the left of a notification, replace this one by your brand icon.
trans-unit.target: `EngagementIconNotification.png` : The brand icon displayed at the left of a notification, replace this one by your brand icon.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementIconOk.png` : The "Ok" icon of the reach pages ApplicationBar.
trans-unit.target: `EngagementIconOk.png` : The "Ok" icon of the reach pages ApplicationBar.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementIconCancel.png` : The "Cancel" icon of the reach pages ApplicationBar.
trans-unit.target: `EngagementIconCancel.png` : The "Cancel" icon of the reach pages ApplicationBar.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementIconCloseLight.png` : The "Close" icon of the Mobile Engagement's reach notification for the Windows Phone light theme.
trans-unit.target: `EngagementIconCloseLight.png` : The "Close" icon of the Mobile Engagement's reach notification for the Windows Phone light theme.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementIconCloseDark.png` : The "Close" icon of the Mobile Engagement's reach notification for the Windows Phone dark theme.
trans-unit.target: `EngagementIconCloseDark.png` : The "Close" icon of the Mobile Engagement's reach notification for the Windows Phone dark theme.

trans-unit.source: `EngagementConfiguration.xml` : The Mobile Engagement's configuration file, this is where you can customize Engagement settings (Engagement connection string, report crashes etc).
trans-unit.target: `EngagementConfiguration.xml` : The Mobile Engagement's configuration file, this is where you can customize Engagement settings (Engagement connection string, report crashes etc).
